@page
@model LoginModel

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Inicio de Sesi\u00f3n";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <section>
            <form id="account" method="post">
                <h4>Inicie Sesi&oacute;n con sus credenciales</h4>
                <hr />
                <div asp-validation-summary="All" class="text-danger"></div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label asp-for="Input.Email">Correo Electr&oacute;nico</label>
                    <input asp-for="Input.Email" class="form-control" />
                    <span asp-validation-for="Input.Email" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label asp-for="Input.Password">Contrase&ntilde;a</label>
                    <input asp-for="Input.Password" class="form-control" />
                    <span asp-validation-for="Input.Password" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <div class="checkbox">
                        <label asp-for="Input.RememberMe">
                            <input asp-for="Input.RememberMe" />
                            ¿Recordarme?
                        </label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Iniciar Sesi&oacute;n</button>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <p>
                        <a id="forgot-password" asp-page="./ForgotPassword">¿Olvid&oacute; su contrase&ntilde;a?</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </form>
        </section>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-2">
        <section>
            <h4>Info</h4>
            <hr />
                <div>
                    <p>
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut nibh tellus, dapibus sit amet porttitor nec, rutrum in quam. Aliquam commodo aliquam magna eu hendrerit. Fusce vestibulum lobortis tempor. Integer faucibus, odio et tempor sagittis, erat sapien aliquet lorem, id sodales lectus velit eget nisi. Curabitur vitae velit sit amet metus eleifend efficitur in et nibh. Praesent odio nibh, posuere quis nibh eget, fringilla imperdiet ante. Aenean non ultricies augue, eget mollis nisi. Sed finibus leo et semper interdum. Praesent sagittis mattis sollicitudin. In hac habitasse platea dictumst.
                    </p>
                </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    <partial name="_ValidationScriptsPartial" />
}
